INSERT INTO `global` VALUES (1,'published','2024-10-11 19:06:52','2024-11-19 16:45:25','Floppy Hammer','The Floppy Hammer is exactly what it sounds like: a hammer made entirely out of a soft, pliable, pink silicone. Originally created as an art object, the Floppy Hammer has become the perfect white elephant gift, humorous home decoration, or unexpected addition to your toolbox. It is the perfect gift for the person that has everything. ','1884e0d2-1a3c-4c0b-8df5-1ed537fd62ec','980','100','090974f0-0f66-48bb-abc3-80118e27ed58','Floppy Hammer, White elephant, gift, gag gift, housewarming, tool, fun gift, silly gift, cool gift, weird gift,  Useless tool, Art object, Fidget device, Eyebrow raiser, Conversation starter, Inside joke, Table topper, Jiggle generator, Thought provoker, Mindless entertainment, Wrist workout, Office distraction, Impulse buy, Head scratcher, Attention grabber, Flip flopper, Shelf oddity, Novelty gift, Imagination sparker, Stress reliever, Collector’s item, Procrastination assistant, Obvious imposter, gift for any age, gift for anyone\n\nTheoretically helpful. Literally ridiculous. \n\nFor all your floppy needs.\n\nA powder pink hammer that wiggles when you wave it. Put it on your desk for inspiration breaks, bring it out at a dinner party for laughs, or give it as a housewarming gift...even if it\'s for your own house.\n\nThe Floppy Hammer is exactly what it sounds like: a hammer made entirely out of a soft, pliable, pink silicone. Originally created as an art object by Olivia de Salve Villedieu in 2019, this useless tool flops around when you try to use it and anyone that uses it can’t help but laugh. Earlier iterations made appearances on Olivia\'s coffee table and at her dinner parties, where they were instant conversation starters. It quickly became clear that this hammer sparks joy, and we always need a little more of that. The Floppy Hammer is the perfect housewarming gift, humorous home decoration, or unexpected addition to your toolbox. It is the perfect gift for the person that has everything. ','11650215-89ef-4e1b-b183-dbf76ce32a55','5273ac21-bacb-40bb-85ea-cc043d0f7af7','679','705');
